### FastAPI Control Backend - Example Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@apiPrefix = /api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/health

### Get Latest Mock Data (generated every 2 seconds)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/latest

### Send Motor Status (optional - mock data generator handles this)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/motor-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rpm": 4800,
  "torque": 1.3,
  "load": 72.4,
  "temperature": 42.7
}

### Send Vibration Metrics (optional - mock data generator handles this)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/vibration-metrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "main_freq": 256.0,
  "amplitude": 0.32,
  "rms": 0.15,
  "impulse_count": 4
}

### Set Control Parameters - Speed Mode
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/set-parameters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "speed",
  "target_rpm": 5000,
  "target_torque": null
}

### Set Control Parameters - Torque Mode
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/set-parameters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "torque",
  "target_rpm": null,
  "target_torque": 1.5
}

### Set Control Parameters - Torque Mode (alternative)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/control/set-parameters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "torque",
  "target_torque": 1.8
}
